OL,3,CMurder probe launched in Reading after
OL,4,Cfatal stabbing
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched in Reading following a fatal
OL,8,Fstabbing in a residential area.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to an alleyway in
OL,11,FLower Earley on Saturday afternoon
OL,12,Ffollowing multiple reports that a man
OL,13,Fin his twenties had been seriously
OL,14,Finjured.
OL,16,FOfficers attended alongside other
OL,17,Fmedical professionals, and the man was
OL,18,Ftaken to hospital where he later died.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
