OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779635466
OL,3,CMurder probe launched in Reading after
OL,4,Cfatal stabbing
OL,6,FThames Valley Police said the man's
OL,7,Fnext of kin have been informed, but
OL,8,Fformal identification and post-mortem
OL,9,Fprocesses are yet to be completed.
OL,11,FA scene watch is currently in place in
OL,12,Fthe alleyway between Cutbush Lane and
OL,13,FKensington Close and through to the
OL,14,Falley between Cutbush Lane and Gypsy
OL,15,FLane.
OL,17,FA teenage boy, from Reading, has been
OL,18,Farrested on suspicion of murder and
OL,19,Fremains in police custody.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
