PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779635466
OL,3,CMurder probe launched in Reading after
OL,4,Cfatal stabbing
OL,6,FSenior investigating officer Detective
OL,7,FInspector Nick Hind, of the Major
OL,8,FCrime Unit said: "Our thoughts remain
OL,9,Fwith the man's next of kin following
OL,10,Fhis death.
OL,12,F"We understand this murder will be of
OL,13,Fconcern to the community, but we do
OL,14,Fnot believe there is any threat to the
OL,15,Fwider public.
OL,17,F"We are in the early stages of a
OL,18,Fcomplex investigation, but we are
OL,19,Ffollowing several lines of enquiry to
OL,20,Festablish the full circumstances
OL,21,Faround the murder.
OL,26,@pD@ROUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
