FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779635466
OL,3,CMurder probe launched in Reading after
OL,4,Cfatal stabbing
OL,6,F"Members of the public are likely to
OL,7,Fsee an increased police presence in
OL,8,Fthe area while we investigate, and we
OL,9,Fwould advise anyone with any concerns
OL,10,Fto please speak to one of our
OL,11,Funiformed officers.
OL,13,F"I would ask that at this time people
OL,14,Frefrain from speculation on social
OL,15,Fmedia or other mediums whilst we
OL,16,Finvestigate to find the truth behind
OL,17,Fthis incident and loss of life."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
